        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Southwestern Oregon Watershed and Salmon Protection Act of 2021</b></p> <p>This bill withdraws specified federal land in Curry and Josephine Counties in Oregon from (1) entry, appropriation, or disposal under the public land laws; (2) location, entry, and patent under the mining laws; and (3) operation under the mineral leasing and geothermal leasing laws. </p>  ]]>
        </text>
